caption:
There’s nothing like God molding your character into who you were always meant to be. 
.
.
.
He will dig deep into your heart and PULL OUT your true identity. 
.
.
God is calling you into deeper levels of honesty with Him and yourself. But if all you’ve ever known is “conditional love”…? 
.
.
Where you’re working yourself half to death and trying to find your worth in what you DO for God and people? 
.
.
.
You’ll miss the real lesson. God loves you & wants you and Him to connect… and actually feel what it’s like to BE ONE with God
.
.
Yes God has a purpose for your life. But you’re a being BEFORE you have a purpose 
.
.
.
